{"tid":2089352,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被問及若被「送中」會否被判死刑 鄭若驊：我管唔到","createTime":"2020-07-01T15:27:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T02:35:21.000Z","uid":212626,"like":55,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"f392c36bcd08160e539e66f03a94a4460f79dd68","tid":2089352,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:27:43.000Z","msg":"有傳媒也問及若疑犯因違國安法被「送中」，會否被判死刑？鄭若驊亦未有保證，直指：「<span style=\"color: red;\">這已非香港所管，所以內地怎處理不是香港可干預。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n至於《國安法》提到違法者可被DQ、卻未有提到期限，是否意味如內地的「剝奪政治權利終身」？鄭亦說不出所以然，指《國安法》「無話喪失（參選資格）幾耐」，但「可以有機會被視為終身呢」，然後強調現時是關乎危害國家安全的問題，是「非常極之嚴重嘅罪行」。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200701/PCUUXHFKTCXIEP4HC6FW3JPN2A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200701%2FPCUUXHFKTCXIEP4HC6FW3JPN2A%2F&d=Ia4lQUE8yf8cF0bf%2B23B9YGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=94826686\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200701%2FPCUUXHFKTCXIEP4HC6FW3JPN2A%2F&h=6bf92ee4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200701/PCUUXHFKTCXIEP4HC6FW3JPN2A/</a><br />\n骹主<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cc588f16fecc4dbeff3450e94a7005359af381d","tid":2089352,"uid":66202,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:29:40.000Z","msg":"香港恢復死刑啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c346ab231da95e20057b4b9855c7878ad2c08a49","tid":2089352,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:31:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de24090a5b5c041fd043d5b4ef67e297ab246f7f","tid":2089352,"uid":205162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:36:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"